This app was designed to help track your daily toDo activates best way as possible, to keep track on your task,
in this app you can add as many tasks you want set statuses in your preference for example (new, pending, postponed and done),
after you finish your task you can delete them, 
you can also search your task in the list this is very helpful if you looking for particular task in the list.
Hopefully app is fun to use and enjoy using it.
Thanks.
